summary: Retex of the companion dog to a red-brown color.
descriptionHtml:
I couldn\'t find a dog retex mod that had the color I was going for... a nice red-brown like an old hound dog, so I just went and re-colored it myself.  I also added some black around the muzzle, because what outdoor dog hasn\'t dyed its mouth black with all the stuff it sticks its nose into?  ;p

Just extract into your Skyrim Data folder.
author: trixterpriest
